headline: Keysight Completes Industry-First PSA Certified Level 4 Evaluation for Silicon Labs’ SiXG301 SoC
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., August 21, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) has completed the industry's first PSA Certified Level 4 security evaluation for Silicon Labs’ Series 3 Secure Vault™ on the SixG301 wireless SoC, marking a significant advancement in the security assurance of connected devices.
